examples.full_tag: <ref>It should be noted that in the otherwise excellent edition of Baer the word {{lang|he|חק‎}} has been omitted by mistake in [[../Proverbs#5:20|Proverbs v. 20]]. In [[../Ezekiel#9:9|Ezekiel ix. 9]] the Board deviated from the Baer edition and accepted the reading {{lang|he|דמים‎}} instead of {{lang|he|חמס‎}}. In [[../Psalms#62:4|Psalm lxii. 4]] the vocalization of Ben Naphtali was followed instead of that of Ben Asher usually adopted by Baer.</ref>
examples.contents: It should be noted that in the otherwise excellent edition of Baer the word {{lang|he|חק‎}} has been omitted by mistake in [[../Proverbs#5:20|Proverbs v. 20]]. In [[../Ezekiel#9:9|Ezekiel ix. 9]] the Board deviated from the Baer edition and accepted the reading {{lang|he|דמים‎}} instead of {{lang|he|חמס‎}}. In [[../Psalms#62:4|Psalm lxii. 4]] the vocalization of Ben Naphtali was followed instead of that of Ben Asher usually adopted by Baer.
